		(SELECT page_id, GROUP_CONCAT(CONCAT_WS(":: ",page_attribute_key,page_attribute_value) SEPARATOR "|") as attributes FROM page_attributes as attr GROUP BY page_id ORDER BY page_id )
		AS subs ON p.id = subs.page_id

		SELECT p.id as page_id, p.*, subs.* FROM page as p INNER JOIN 
		(SELECT page_id, GROUP_CONCAT(CONCAT_WS(":: ",page_attribute_key,page_attribute_value) SEPARATOR "|") as attributes FROM page_attributes as attr GROUP BY page_id ORDER BY page_id )
		AS subs ON p.id = subs.page_id

		(SELECT page_id, GROUP_CONCAT(CONCAT_WS(":: ",page_attribute_key,page_attribute_value) SEPARATOR "|") as attributes FROM page_attributes as attr GROUP BY page_id ORDER BY page_id )
		AS subs ON p.id = subs.page_id
